<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Verify Your Payment PIN</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.1);
      border-left: 6px solid #1720a1f2;
    }
    .header {
      font-size: 22px;
      color: #1720a1f2;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .otp-box {
      background-color: #f1fdf3;
      padding: 16px;
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: #1720a1f2;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">üîê Confirm Your OTP</div>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Use the OTP below to verify you own this account. This code is valid for 10 minutes:</p>

    <div class="otp-box">{{otp_code}}</div>

    <p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email or contact <a href="{{support_link}}">support</a>.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      Thanks for transacting with Xnyder.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
